      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that balances mechanical integrity with refined aesthetics. This unit has been subjected to a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure optimal performance and safety standards. The exterior retains a professional finish, complemented by a well-appointed interior that reflects consistent care. Offering a sophisticated driving experience and proven reliability, this vehicle represents an exceptional acquisition for the discerning motorist seeking both quality and value.",
