    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_23_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_23",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, impressive shine, showing only the minor, honest road wear expected of a well-cared-for driver. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features upholstery that remains firm and supportive, with all digital displays and convenience features functioning exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has followed a strict service schedule, resulting in a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive, quiet engine. Whether you're looking for a reliable commuter or a weekend tourer, this car offers a complete, turn-key experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
