    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This specimen offers a balanced driving experience, featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain suited for the discerning driver. We invite you to experience a standard of excellence that commands respect on the road.",
